{"tid":570122,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚發夢夢見莊思敏, 想同大家分享一下","createTime":"2018-02-23T10:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T04:58:54.000Z","uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9df4953adda37503126271e88f955b093e4026c6","tid":570122,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T10:38:11.000Z","msg":"我夢見自己同佢喺一個沙灘<br />\n沙灘上面得我地兩個人, 同埋我地各自騎住嘅馬(唔記得咩顏色)<br />\n地上面好多蘋果, 兩隻馬行一步就停低食一個, 行一步, 食一個<br />\n我問莊思敏(敏敏)而家係幾年幾月<br />\n佢望住一分鐘, 佢對眼好藍, 眼神自信但憂傷, 跟住用一口英女皇式口音答我: &quot;<em>Eternity</em>&quot;<br />\n之後佢向住個海係咁跑, 我騎住隻馬追, 追追下就扎醒左<br />\n就係咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想知更多嘅下次再同大家講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1f5ca9c7f689c51198304bb6d6faa76568ce0d","tid":570122,"uid":42407,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T10:38:41.000Z","msg":"無甜，0分"},{"pid":"d93be9e65d5cd2885f066919d04ffd80f8263485","tid":570122,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd1f5ca9c7f689c51198304bb6d6faa76568ce0d","tid":570122,"uid":42407,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T10:38:41.000Z","msg":"無甜，0分"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T10:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd984b3324ed3e1ca03e80e56c3b24532e087368","tid":570122,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T10:43:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無甜，0分</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote>"},{"pid":"ffcd6d54ebbdc32dcbd3822140883d8371cd3981","tid":570122,"uid":48577,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T10:43:57.000Z","msg":"你到底有幾撚鍾意莊思敏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c5a544ec8a753e54cf056310b1a8466bf90ebb","tid":570122,"uid":120399,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018